Project Overview

Project Name: Coffee Shop Mobile App (React Native / Stripe Payments)
Description:
A mobile e-commerce app for coffee products that allows users to browse products, add them to cart, manage favorites, and complete orders with Stripe payment integration.

Technologies Used

React Native & Expo – for cross-platform mobile app development (iOS & Android).

React Navigation – for stack navigation between screens.

Zustand – for state management (cart, orders, search).

Stripe React Native SDK – to handle secure payments.

Axios / Fetch – to communicate with backend API.

Expo LinearGradient & Vector Icons – UI enhancements and icons.

App Features

Home Screen

Displays coffee categories and products.

Search functionality for products by name.

Product Detail Screen

Shows product information and price.

Add product to cart with quantity management.

Cart / Shopping Bag Screen

Lists all added products with total price calculation.

Allows checkout with Stripe Payment Sheet.

Favorites Screen

Users can save favorite products for later.

Stripe Payment Integration

Secure checkout using Payment Sheet.

Handles various payment methods.

Shows order confirmation after successful payment.

State Management

Cart and order management using Zustand.

Persistent and reactive updates of product quantity.

Project Tools & Tech Stack
Core

React Native 0.79.2 – cross-platform mobile development

Expo 53.0.7 – app development and build tooling

React 19.0.0 – UI library

Navigation

@react-navigation/native – routing & navigation

@react-navigation/native-stack – stack-based navigation

State Management

Zustand 4.5.2 – global state for cart, orders, and favorites

UI & Styling

expo-linear-gradient – gradients for headers & backgrounds

@expo/vector-icons / react-native-vector-icons – icons

expo-font / expo-asset – custom fonts and assets management

expo-status-bar – status bar management

Backend & API

Axios 1.6.8 – API requests for products and order handling

Payments

@stripe/stripe-react-native 0.45.0 – Stripe Payment Sheet integration

@stripe/stripe-terminal-react-native 0.0.1-beta.17 – optional Stripe terminal support

